 DANGOTE Cement Plc will begin the Season 2 of its Bag of Goodies national consumer promo this month. In the Season 1 of the promo, 40 lucky individuals across Nigeria got a brand new saloon car each. The previous winners of the star prizes expressed gratitude to the company for transforming their lives. During the Season 2, at least 1,000 Nigerians are expected to win the star prize of N1 million each in the promo that will last 16 weeks. Other prizes include tricycles, refrigerators, television sets, generators, Goodies packs, smaller monetary prizes and airtime.